libpst-win64
============

Full documentation is in README.md (rendered on the project's GitHub page):
a Windows readpst.exe build, the libpst_py Python library, and the
fuzz-hardening/CI work this fork adds on top of pst-format/libpst.

Building the tools from source (autotools, as upstream):

    ./configure --enable-python=no --enable-dii=no
    make
    make install

Building the Python library (libpst_py):

    pip install .

See README.md for prerequisites, installation from prebuilt wheels, usage,
and the security/fuzzing setup.

